           <app><note>Text is from Manganaro in ASNP 1977. The main alternative is Comparetti's editio princeps in NotScav 1912.</note></app>
           <app><note>C. adds two speculatively restored lines before the first preserved line: <supplied reason="lost">πεπρᾶσθαι Δίωνι τοῦ δεῖνος τὸ τοῦ δεῖνος τοῦ δεῖνος ἐν</supplied></note></app>
